data.description: WELCOME HOME! Enjoy this Lovey, Tropical Paradise & Private Balcony. VERY CLEAN AND REFRESHING!  Large tile flooring matches throughout! Great open kitchen, vastly inviting living room & dining area.  Features a split floor plan! Grand Owner’s Suite has a private bath & custom walk-in closet.   Spacious Guest Bedroom w/ large closet & full guest bathroom. Offers a Private Laundry Room w/ utility closet.  White Decorative Interior Window Treatments Throughout. BEST AMMENITES!  New Elevator, Pool & Sauna, Tiki Bar, BBQ Grills, Bird & Wildlife Sanctuary, Clubhouse, Library, Game Room, Event Kitchen, Private Hall, Tennis, Gym, Playground, Basketball and Gym.  Nearby Beaches, Golf, Casino, Shops & Dining!  All ages, Pet Friendly, Tons of Guest Parking!  EXCELLENT for Entertaining!
